IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. MATH-OP.

DATA DIVISION.
01 A PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 B PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 C PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 D PICTURE IS 9(3).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MOVE 10 TO A
    MOVE 20 TO B
    ADD A TO B
    MULTIPLY 3 BY A GIVING C
    SUBTRACT 5 FROM B GIVING D
    DIVIDE 2 INTO C.
